{"tid":2444571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耳濡目染｜英研究：女童多玩激瘦洋娃娃 容易對自己身體形象有負面想法","createTime":"2021-03-13T02:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T07:52:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d9d6968d7868ab187e383df57fb6c812b9e79c","tid":2444571,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"英國一項研究指出，如果女童經常玩身型超瘦的洋娃娃，容易對自己身材或身體形象有負面想法，並渴望自己亦擁有像洋娃娃般的不真實纖瘦身材。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員找來30名5至9歲的女童參與研究，詢問她們喜愛和理想的身材，然後再安排她們玩超瘦或真實身材的公仔。女童玩公仔5分鐘後，再回答之前有關她們喜愛和理想身材的相同問題。結果顯示，曾玩超瘦公仔的女童，她們理想的自我體重指數（Body Mass Index，BMI）顯著下降，而玩普通公仔的女童的答案則沒有顯著變化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210312/LGO3AY33FZC2BPNSAMTBPIMDXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210312%2FLGO3AY33FZC2BPNSAMTBPIMDXM%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=d77830e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210312%2FLGO3AY33FZC2BPNSAMTBPIMDXM%2F&h=97b2dee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210312/LGO3AY33FZC2BPNSAMTBPIMDXM/</a>"},{"pid":"fdfc1f79f32f6c2ac1cd6dc08025108156ac153d","tid":2444571,"uid":69753,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:23:58.000Z","msg":"咁要出多啲肥婆TB公仔喇"},{"pid":"4ddaf98c631bdb3d6522deae96993cc75e858a9e","tid":2444571,"uid":19213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"除左blm<br />\n仲有flm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠cls"},{"pid":"8a757ee73b834b06c6b3fa9ec718ea6c074b0aba","tid":2444571,"uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"fdfc1f79f32f6c2ac1cd6dc08025108156ac153d","tid":2444571,"uid":69753,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:23:58.000Z","msg":"咁要出多啲肥婆TB公仔喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: